<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr" style="font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 14px; margin: 0;">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>OptiRH - Nouvelle réponse à votre réclamation</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="{{ absolute_url('/css/email.css') }}">
</head>

<body style="font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 14px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; -webkit-text-size-adjust: none; width: 100% !important; height: 100%; line-height: 1.6em; background-color: #f6f6f6; margin: 0;" bgcolor="#f6f6f6">
    <table class="body-wrap" style="font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 14px; width: 100%; background-color: #f6f6f6; margin: 0;" bgcolor="#f6f6f6">
        <tr style="font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 14px; margin: 0;">
            <td style="font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: top; margin: 0;" valign="top"></td>
            <td class="container" width="1100" style="font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: top; display: block !important; max-width: 600px !important; clear: both !important; margin: 0 auto;" valign="top">
                <div class="content" style="font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 14px; max-width: 800px; display: block; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px;">
                    <table class="main" width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 14px; border-radius: 3px; margin: 0; border: none;">
                        <tr style="font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 14px; margin: 0;">
                            <td class="content-wrap" style="font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: top; margin: 0; padding: 30px; border: 3px solid #4fc6e1; border-radius: 7px; background-color: #fff;" valign="top">
                                <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 14px; margin: 0;">
                                    <tr>
                                        <td style="text-align: center">
                                            <a href="{{ absolute_url('home') }}" style="display: block; margin-bottom: 10px;">
                                                <img src="https://i.ibb.co/0yTLr7bq/408065252-0f3bdb15-6321-42da-b294-c12b76d025d3.png" height="140" alt="logo"/>
                                            </a>
                                            <br/>
                                            <br/>
                                        </td>
                                    </tr>
                                    <tr style="font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 14px; margin: 0;">
                                        <td class="content-block" style="font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: top; margin: 0; padding: 0 0 20px;" valign="top">
                                            <h1 style="font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 20px; font-weight: bold; margin: 0;">Bonjour {{ employeur.nom }},</h1>
                                            <p style="font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 14px; margin: 0;">
                                                Une nouvelle réponse a été ajoutée à votre réclamation concernant "{{ reclamation.type }}".
                                            </p>
                                        </td>
                                    </tr>
                                    <tr style="font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 14px; margin: 0;">
                                        <td class="content-block" style="font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: top; margin: 0; padding: 0 0 20px; background-color: #f9f9f9; border-left: 4px solid #4fc6e1;" valign="top">
                                            <h2 style="font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-weight: bold; margin: 0 0 10px 0;">Détails de la réponse :</h2>
                                            <p style="font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 14px; margin: 0 0 10px 0;">
                                                {{ reponse.description }}
                                            </p>
                                            <p style="font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 14px; margin: 0;">
                                                <strong>Date de la réponse :</strong> {{ reponse.date|date('d/m/Y H:i') }}
                                            </p>
                                        </td>
                                    </tr>
                                    <tr style="font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 14px; margin: 0;">
                                        <td class="content-block" style="font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: top; margin: 0; padding: 0 0 20px;" valign="top">
                                            <p style="font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 14px; margin: 0;">
                                                Vous pouvez consulter votre réclamation et cette réponse en vous connectant à votre espace.
                                            </p>
                                            <p style="font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 14px; margin: 20px 0 0 0;">
                                                Si vous avez des questions ou des problèmes, n'hésitez pas à nous contacter :
                                                <a href="mailto:support@optirh.fr" style="font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 14px; color: #6658dd; text-decoration: none; font-weight: bold;">support@optirh.fr</a>.
                                            </p>
                                        </td>
                                    </tr>
                                    <tr style="font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 14px; margin: 0;">
                                        <td class="content-block" style="font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: top; margin: 0; padding: 0 0 20px;" valign="top">
                                            Cordialement,<br>
                                            <br/>
                                            —
                                            <b>OptiRH</b>
                                            - Nexus Team
                                        </td>
                                    </tr>
                                </table>
                            </td>
                        </tr>
                    </table>
                </div>
            </td>
            <td style="font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: top; margin: 0;" valign="top"></td>
        </tr>
    </table>
</body>
</html>